videos.description: Jordan Bowden knocks down a wide open 3-pointer as the Volunteers roll in the first half.
videos.headline: Tennessee's Bowden sinks corner 3

videos.description: Devontae Shuler climbs the ladder to throw down the fastbreak alley-oop for the Rebels.
videos.headline: Ole Miss' Shuler slams home alley-oop

videos.description: Terence Davis stuffs in a two-handed jam as the Rebels storm back to close the gap early in the second half.
videos.headline: Ole Miss' Davis gets all the way up

videos.description: Lamonte Turner knocks down a shot from beyond the arc as the Vols regain control midway in the second half.
videos.headline: Tennessee's Turner sinks 3-pointer

videos.description: Behind Admiral Schofield's 25 points and Lamonte Turner's 13 off the bench, the No. 19 Vols defeat the Rebels 73-65.
videos.headline: Tennessee tops Ole Miss
